  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. Intended use is pre-market submission support for a Class II spinal fixation device; the model is used to predict construct stiffness and yield load under compression-bending per ASTM F1717. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) is below required level due to a single test condition being evaluated.",
